<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الصفة التاسعة:</span> الإذلاق <span class="c2">(١)</span>:<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١ - معناه لغة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
